  <title>Tinkering</title>
  <description>Tinkering</description>
  <content>&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-family: comic sans ms,sans-serif;"&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: x-small;"&gt;&lt;span style="font-family: tahoma,arial,helvetica,sans-serif;"&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: small;"&gt;Ultimamente tenho me encontrado muito com esta palavra !&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-family: comic sans ms,sans-serif;"&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: x-small;"&gt;&lt;span style="font-family: tahoma,arial,helvetica,sans-serif;"&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: small;"&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Tinkering&lt;/strong&gt; - &lt;em&gt;[ting-que-ring]&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-family: comic sans ms,sans-serif;"&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: x-small;"&gt;&lt;span style="font-family: tahoma,arial,helvetica,sans-serif;"&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: small;"&gt;Tinkering &amp;eacute; o que acontece quando voc&amp;ecirc; tenta fazer alguma coisa que geralmente n&amp;atilde;o sabe como fazer, tem uma vontade s&amp;uacute;bita&amp;nbsp;de fazer algo usando sua&amp;nbsp;imagina&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o e curiosidade.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-family: comic sans ms,sans-serif;"&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: x-small;"&gt;&lt;span style="font-family: tahoma,arial,helvetica,sans-serif;"&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: small;"&gt;Quando voc&amp;ecirc; &lt;em&gt;"tinker" &lt;/em&gt;n&amp;atilde;o h&amp;aacute; instru&amp;ccedil;&amp;otilde;es - mas tamb&amp;eacute;m n&amp;atilde;o h&amp;aacute; falhas, nem jeito certo ou errado de fazer uma coisa. &amp;Eacute; entender como as coisas funcionam e como fazer elas trabalharem de uma forma nova ou diferente.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-family: comic sans ms,sans-serif;"&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: x-small;"&gt;&lt;span style="font-family: tahoma,arial,helvetica,sans-serif;"&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: small;"&gt;Fazer objetos que aparentemente n&amp;atilde;o combinam (como um&amp;nbsp;tal&amp;atilde;o de pedidos&amp;nbsp;e um telefone celular) trabalharem de forma harmoniosa.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-family: comic sans ms,sans-serif;"&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: x-small;"&gt;&lt;span style="font-family: tahoma,arial,helvetica,sans-serif;"&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: small;"&gt;&lt;em&gt;Tinkering&lt;/em&gt;&amp;nbsp;&amp;eacute; na sua forma mais b&amp;aacute;sica, um processo que&amp;nbsp;une&amp;nbsp;divers&amp;atilde;o com conhecimento.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-family: comic sans ms,sans-serif;"&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: x-small;"&gt;&lt;span style="font-family: tahoma,arial,helvetica,sans-serif;"&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: small;"&gt;... o que me faz pensar que&amp;nbsp;aprendi uma&amp;nbsp;palavra s&amp;oacute;, que define o processo de cria&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o que h&amp;aacute; muitos anos adoto na minha vida, no trabalho e&amp;nbsp;na True Systems.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-family: comic sans ms,sans-serif;"&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: x-small;"&gt;&lt;span style="font-family: tahoma,arial,helvetica,sans-serif;"&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: small;"&gt;&amp;Eacute; uma palavra nova em seu sentido, mas muito antiga.&amp;nbsp;A defini&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o mais antiga que achei, de 1658&amp;nbsp;: "manter-se ocupado fazendo algo sem utilidade".&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-family: comic sans ms,sans-serif;"&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: x-small;"&gt;&lt;span style="font-family: tahoma,arial,helvetica,sans-serif;"&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: small;"&gt;Os tempos mudam, as pessoas mudam ... e a tecnologia ... j&amp;aacute; mudou ao piscar dos olhos !&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-family: comic sans ms,sans-serif;"&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: x-small;"&gt;&lt;span style="font-family: tahoma,arial,helvetica,sans-serif;"&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: small;"&gt;Happy Tinkering &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
